        {
            "title": "兩新股破底 天域半導體挫30%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>香港周五（5日）有兩隻新股登場，惟首日掛牌雙雙潛水。內地現代中式麵館餐飲集團遇見小麵（02408）曾低見4.98元，較招股價7.04元，一度大跌29.3%，收市報5.08元，下挫27.8%。一手500股，賬面蝕980元。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">同日掛牌的內地碳化硅外延片製造商天域半導體（02658）低見38元，較招股價58元，下挫34.5%，收市報40.5元，跌30.2%。一手50股，賬面蝕875元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>卓越睿新暗盤飆三成 賺二千</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於下周一（8日）掛牌的納芯微（02676），周五暗盤亦插水。該股在富途暗盤收報105.7元，較發售價116元跌8.88%或10.3元，一手100股，賬面蝕1030元。配發結果顯示，納芯微公開發售接獲2.19萬份有效申請，超購24.33倍，一手中籤率4.32%，認購25手（2500股）穩中一手；國際發售超購1.65倍。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-974f15f2-b73e-369e-bed4-32e60c95dc1d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">卓越睿新（02687）周五暗盤造好，該股在富途暗盤收報87.55元，較發售價67.5元抽高29.7%或20.05元，一手100股，賬面賺2005元。配發結果顯示，公開發售接獲13.52萬份有效申請，超購4812.4倍，一手中籤率1%；國際發售超購1.33倍。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其他新股消息方面，京東工業（07618）下周一截飛，截至周五晚10時，券商暫時為其借出142.6億元孖展，按公開發售集資額3.27億元計，相當於超額認購逾42倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>HashKey傳下周招股籌15.6億</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博引述消息指出，香港持牌虛擬資產交易平台HashKey Exchange的母公司HashKey Holdings最快下周開始招股，計劃至少籌集2億美元（15.6億港元）。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A9%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1%E7%A0%B4%E5%BA%95-%E5%A4%A9%E5%9F%9F%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8E%E9%AB%94%E6%8C%AB30-182300936.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-06 02:25:50",
